1. *Beše* mu očajno potrebno pomoći da bi spasio svoj život. (He desperately needed help to save his life.)
2. *Beše* joj zabranjeno da se približi tom mestu. (She was forbidden to approach that place.)
3. *Beše* to veoma težak period za njih dvoje. (It was a very hard period for the two of them.)
4. *Beše* to jedinstveno iskustvo koje će se pamtiti. (It was a unique experience to remember.)
5. *Beše* mu potrebno da prođe kroz mnogo iskušenja. (He had to go through many temptations.)